claw.tatsu.xcodeml.xnode.fortran

Class FbasicType

  • java.lang.Object
    • claw.tatsu.xcodeml.xnode.common.Xnode
      • claw.tatsu.xcodeml.xnode.fortran.FbasicType

  • public class FbasicType
extends Xnode
    The FbasicType represents the FbasicType (3.3) element in XcodeML intermediate representation.

    Elements: (kind?, (len | (arrayIndex | indexRange)+)?, coShape?) - Optional: - kind - len - arrayIndex - indexRange - coShape TODO not needed for the moment Attributes: - Required: type (text), ref (text) - Optional: is_public (bool), is_private (bool), is_pointer (bool), is_target (bool), is_external (bool),is_intrinsic (bool), is_optional (bool), is_save (bool), is_parameter (bool), is_allocatable (bool), intent (text: in, out, inout)
